author.bio:
Author of THE NEVERLAND WARS, a YA fantasy novel and modern day continuation of the Peter Pan story, available for preorder now. Her other books, short stories, flash fiction, and poems can be found on audreygreathouse.com

Audrey Greathouse is a lost child in a perpetual footloose quest for her own post-adolescent Neverland. Originally from Seattle, she earned her BA in English literature online from Southern New Hampshire University while backpacking the west coast. A pianist, circus artist, fire-eater, street mime, swing dancer, and novelist, she has warn many hats as an artist and now resides in Silicon Valley's San Jose.
